Package: huncMarkovDMSS
Title: Diffuse Mucosal Sclerosis Syndrome Cost-Effectiveness Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ian", "Cromwell",
           email = "healthyuncertainty@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: An interactive multi-comparator Markov cohort model for
    cost-effectiveness analysis of Cardivex, Zonapride, Septoplasty, and
    Ablatherm versus Standard of Care in patients with Diffuse Mucosal
    Sclerosis Syndrome (DMSS). Implements a 4-state population proportion
    model with frozen grade distributions, 4-week cycles, age-dependent
    background mortality, perioperative mortality for surgical arms,
    probabilistic sensitivity analysis across 23 parameters, and an
    interactive Shiny application. Developed as a fictional illustrative
    example for the HEPackageR skill validation exercise.
